        <section>
            <p>For many years this website used its <em>colophon</em> as an "about me" page, rather than about PhotoGabble. Today the <a href="/about/">about page</a> takes that role leaving this page to its correct intent as an imprint for the publication that is PhotoGabble.</p>
        </section>
